summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of alley in Block Sixty-one (61) A. A. Denny's Addition in the City of Seattle, by paving under Ordinance No. 16543, creating Local Improvement District No. 1529 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
